    {
      "name": "Registro Directo (Legacy)",
      "request": {
        "method": "POST",
        "header": [
          {
            "key": "Content-Type",
            "value": "application/json"
          }
        ],
        "body": {
          "mode": "raw",
          "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"usuario@example.com\",\n  \"password\": \"password123\",\n  \"name\": \"Juan Pérez\"\n}"
        },
        "url": {
          "raw": "http://localhost:3022/auth/register",
          "protocol": "http",
          "host": ["localhost"],
          "port": "3022",
          "path": ["auth", "register"]
        },
        "description": "Registro directo sin verificación por email. Crea el usuario inmediatamente y retorna el JWT token.\n\n**Campos requeridos:**\n- `email`: Email válido del usuario\n- `password`: Mínimo 6 caracteres\n- `name`: Nombre completo del usuario\n\n**Respuesta exitosa:**\n```json\n{\n  \"access_token\": \"jwt_token_here\",\n  \"user\": {\n    \"id\": \"user_id\",\n    \"email\": \"usuario@example.com\",\n    \"name\": \"Juan Pérez\",\n    \"role\": \"customer\"\n  }\n}\n```"
      },
      "response": [
        {
          "name": "Ejemplo de respuesta exitosa",
          "originalRequest": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"usuario@example.com\",\n  \"password\": \"password123\",\n  \"name\": \"Juan Pérez\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "http://localhost:3022/auth/register",
              "protocol": "http",
              "host": ["localhost"],
              "port": "3022",
              "path": ["auth", "register"]
            }
          },
          "status": "OK",
          "code": 200,
          "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
          "header": [
            {
              "key": "Content-Type",
              "value": "application/json"
            }
          ],
          "cookie": [],
